</table></p>
<p>(责编：高红霞、罗昱) </p>
➜旅游名城传帮带 “后进村”蝶变318线上“网红村”
http://www.sohu.com/a/417171194_114731	997
<p>原标题：旅游名城传帮带 “后进村”蝶变318线上“网红村” </p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/598b46e0c5fc4981b00f301fad60edc1.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">成都日报记者在康定采访</p>
<p align="center"><img src="//p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/763fe3980779407e85f0d08e3008aa93.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">杨德伟（中）与村民合影</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200909/554cfca069964fb2a57bd79ab139dbe8.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
